{"title":"fix(remediation): increase mem-load memory limit to prevent OOM kills","body":"Root cause: The mem-load container's memory limit (32Mi) is insufficient for the stress command allocating 50MB, causing repeated OOM kills.

Evidence: Back-off restarting failed container mem-load in pod vigil-app-66f84484b8-kccvb_default(491c71f5-70b7-46dd-85c4-26e0b686ec1f)

Fix: Increased mem-load container memory limit from 32Mi to 64Mi."}
